survey_response.review_text: The doctor explained to me what the issue was and even went an extra mile to show me how it could be prevented and maintained in a healthy manner. She is of a very friendly and cheerful nature. She does her work with utmost dedication and professionalism. She briefs you what she's going to do just before performing the act. This really appealed to me the most,  because it brings about a bonding between you and the doctor.  I definitely recommend others to visit 32T for their dental health problems.

Where should i begin from? perhaps from the beginning. I had major issues with my upper right tooth and the colour of the tooth was pitch black. slowly i realised its decayed and i could not eat anything from that side of my mouth. i met her husband Ashok kamath who was very good professional and successfully finished the first sitting. Then i happened to meet Soumya who greets me with a bright smile and then explained me what the process is going to be. i was very skeptical and nervous but the way she handled it i must say phenominal. Top notch service. i am so brave now that i am ready for rootcanal for all 32 teeth. never knew root canal treatment was this painless. she made it look very easy. she will talk to you like shes your best friend. she will reply to your calls and sms about treatments.Thank you soumya. i am now able to eat anything and everything from right side of my mouth ;-).

I had heard good things about this doctor from my neighborhood, so I had my wisdom tooth extracted also few fillings  and cleaning. Excellent work and there was hardly any pain after the extraction.  I would definitely recommend her  great work, patience and politeness. Moreover She is always available on call to answer any queries related to treatment.
The clinic is small  with two dental chairs but maintained neat and excellent when it comes to hygiene  

Do take appointment to avoid waiting time.

I am very happy with the Doctor's treatment.
She is one of the few Genuine doctors you can find in Bangalore.
I am really happy I found this Doctor.
I had gone for teeth ache, she checked it with proper care and explained to me how this problem can be solved by following the simple technique of flossing.
Now I don't have any teeth ache anymore :-)

We have had an excellent experience with Dr.Soumya in both professional and personal .the way she had  deals with his patients it's great.spl with my kid .she explains and clarifies all the concern very politely that appear practically while in treatment.

Me & my son had root canal  and filling she make sure clinically excellent and update with advance tech. If ur nervous about seeing a dentist I would recommend her any day.

As in the past, experience with Dr Soumya was great. She's experienced, friendly, sincere and explains the procedures well. This time I went for semesterly professional teeth cleaning/scaling after the RCTs that I got done at her clinic effectively in Nov'15.

Highly recommended.

But there is no point in me reading reviews about one doctor and had created expectation to meet the same doctor and to a surprise a new doctor was there. Highly disappointing !

I recommend Dr.sowmya...she is very good in her treatment process & friendly approach  ..I went to the clinic with lot of apprehension for wisdom tooth extraction & tooth filling...she quelled my fear  by explaining whole process & that put me into ease..

I have visited many dental clinics but have not experienced a seamless one. I would recommend her for her friendliness, willingness to explain the root cause,preventional measures and the manner in which she addressed and solved the problem. I would also like to thank the Surgeon who was absolutely amazing in conducting the surgery!
